    "name": "PlanetX",
    "steam_appid": 3309950,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309950/extras/82e150ace0759ae91b3897fa4db725ba.poster.avif?t=1745002893\" width=616 height=190 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309950/extras/82e150ace0759ae91b3897fa4db725ba.webm?t=1745002893\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309950/extras/82e150ace0759ae91b3897fa4db725ba.mp4?t=1745002893\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PlanetX</strong> is a <strong>real-time strategy MMO</strong> that redefines large-scale multiplayer warfare. The battle begins on <strong>Planet Alpha</strong>, where <strong>dozens of players</strong> start with <strong>seven land plots</strong> each. Unlike traditional flat maps, the entire game takes place on a <strong>fully spherical planet</strong>, adding an extra layer of strategy to territorial expansion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309950/extras/ceed1428f9463a035aa8ff4932beb21e.avif?t=1745002893\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309950/extras_big/ceed1428f9463a035aa8ff4932beb21e.avif?t=1745002893 width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players must <strong>build and expand their empire</strong>, constructing various structures and managing resources. The first challenge is achieving a <strong>perfect balance between resource extraction and production</strong> to fuel economic growth. Once a player amasses enough wealth, it's time to <strong>assemble a powerful army</strong>, featuring <strong>tanks, aircraft, and missiles</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309950/extras/291362a3e6c6f9c90fc0a4183cb6ce87.avif?t=1745002893\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309950/extras_big/291362a3e6c6f9c90fc0a4183cb6ce87.avif?t=1745002893 width=800 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A unique aspect of <strong>PlanetX</strong> is its <strong>energy-based warfare </strong>- tanks and aircraft are fully <strong>electric</strong>, requiring <strong>charging stations</strong> before heading into battle. Units will fight until they <strong>run out of energy or are destroyed</strong>, making strategic deployment and resource management crucial.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309950/extras/7c34afb1a6e54e54e8c4012063ff4b36.avif?t=1745002893\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309950/extras_big/7c34afb1a6e54e54e8c4012063ff4b36.avif?t=1745002893 width=800 height=384 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The ultimate goal? <strong>Total planetary domination.</strong> The first player to conquer <strong>every available land plot</strong> on Planet Alpha <strong>claims victory</strong> and earns a <strong>ticket to Planet Beta</strong>, where even greater challenges await. As multiple Alpha champions arrive on Beta, the war escalates to an entirely new level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Everything in <strong>PlanetX </strong>- <strong>construction, battles, resource trading, and land deals - happens in real time</strong>, ensuring a fast-paced, dynamic experience. <strong>Do you have what it takes to rise as the supreme ruler of the galaxy?</strong></p>",
